Class HeadGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.tags.HeadGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    XMLGenerator

    public class HeadGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
implements XMLGenerator
    A class that generates the contents of a web-page <head> element for a page. This may take content from both the configuration and the local page so it is cached in the page request. This allows the surrounding page to add content before the head is generated if requires
